Responsibilities
------------------------------------------------------------------- 
- Analysis and Design of the E-commerce site;
- Project and Team management. Two people in charge: a Designer and a Developer;
- Web site and Server Maintenance;
- Regulate and manage access rights of different users on website;
- Web Design and Web content production;
- Develop of ETL projects for batch loads of the Catalog of products;
- Examine and analyze site traffic;
- Usability Test from different user agents.

Responsibilities as Functional Analyst
------------------------------------------------------------------- 
- Write projects proposals for public and private bids, regarding any GIS aspect involved: technological components needed for the solution, data flows and work planning;
- Write reports about project status, risks and issues; 
- Develop of prototypes;
- Interview with clients to define application requirements;
- Implement final solutions into client offices.

Responsibilities as Data Analyst
------------------------------------------------------------------- 
- Install and configure open source servlets for Spatial Data Infrastructures (SDI);
- Define data model for different business domains;
- Develop of ETL projects. Extract, Transform and Load (ETL) heterogeneous data into DBMS;
- Convert raw data into useful information using different techniques: Zonal statistics, Network analysis, 3D analysis, etc;
- Publish results on Web Services according to OGC standards;
- Data validations according to QA standards;
- Provide with relevant open data to the projects;
- Metadata according to ISO standars.

